&gt; Accept: */*
&gt; 
* Mark bundle as not supporting multiuse
&lt; HTTP/1.1 200 OK
&lt; Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8
&lt; content-length: 18
&lt; 
* Connection #0 to host localhost left intact
{&quot;balance&quot;:123.45}
```

